<codeline lineno="48"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>@param<sp/>obj<sp/>A<sp/>`Meta`<sp/>object<sp/>containing<sp/>the<sp/>`dsid`<sp/>and<sp/>`MetaCachePath`.</highlight></codeline>
