<codeline lineno="59"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>If<sp/>no<sp/>cache<sp/>hit,<sp/>it<sp/>queries<sp/>PyAMI<sp/>using<sp/>`pyAMI_atlas.api.list_datasets`<sp/>and<sp/>`pyAMI_atlas.api.get_file`<sp/>to<sp/>retrieve<sp/>dataset<sp/>and<sp/>file-level<sp/>metadata.<sp/>It<sp/>includes<sp/>a<sp/>retry<sp/>mechanism<sp/>with<sp/>re-authentication<sp/>if<sp/>PyAMI<sp/>calls<sp/>fail.</highlight></codeline>
